item.dc:creator: Allen
item.content:encoded: WooCommerce is built on WordPress that runs 26% of the web. Regularly audited by Sucuri, an industry leader in security, you’re in good hands.

item.title: Sell anything
item.dc:creator: Allen
item.content:encoded: From physical products and digital downloads to subscriptions, content and even appointments, you can sell anything with WooCommerce.

item.title: Worldwide community
item.dc:creator: Allen
item.content:encoded: WooCommerce stores and developers come from all over the world - from Norway to South Africa, from Canada to Japan.

item.title: Content at the core
item.dc:creator: Allen
item.content:encoded: Working on top of the world’s most popular content management system, WooCommerce seamlessly integrates commerce with content. Everything you need is in one place.

item.title: No limits
item.dc:creator: Allen
item.content:encoded: In WooCommerce, you can customize anything and everything. You have complete control, you can add unlimited products and users, and take unlimited orders.

item.title: A modular system
item.dc:creator: Allen
item.content:encoded: WooCommerce is kept lean so you can add the options you want. It’s also made to work alongside your favorite WordPress plugins, so you can keep the features you already love.
